Determine whether this social media post from Donald Trump contains a personal insult to Kamala Harris's intelligence. Simply return "yes" or "no".
content: RT @TeamTrumpPRESIDENT TRUMP: This is the most important election in the history of country. If Kamala Harris gets 4 more years, America as we know it will be DESTROYED. Kamala is openly acknowledged to be the Worst Vice President in History and, as President, she would be even WORSE!
